description: Assemble, configure, and deploy autonomous AI Agents in your browser.
title: AgentGPT
introduction: ResearchGPT is an AI-powered research assistant that helps users generate comprehensive reports on various topics.

faqs.question: Is there a free trial available?
faqs.answer: Yes, there is a free trial period for new users.

faqs.question: Who is the target user of ResearchGPT?
faqs.answer: ResearchGPT is designed for students, researchers, and professionals who need assistance in generating detailed reports.
